::Kluster::

Kluster comes to a stop near a door. He pushes the button, the door opening. 
Kluster steps in.

"Veryfying signature. Signature confirmed." a hidden comp says from the wall, 
the door opening and Kluster entering. "This is the center of the ship," he 
says to Hot Rod, "It only opens to me and Chordate. The storage boxes are 
over there."

He points to a set of drawers against one of the walls. "They will only open 
to me, Chordate, and the signature of the bot who put the object in."

He steps aside, the way clear for Hot Rod to get to the boxes.
